title = "Taking Your Turn"
body_text = "For each turn, each of your units can [color=yellow]move once[/color] and [color=yellow]attack once[/color].

When all of your units have moved and attacked, your turn ends.

When you click on a unit, the [color=blue]BLUE highlights[/color] are the tiles that the unit can go to. Click on any of them to move the unit to that tile.

